text: Located just off a paved, plowed highway and only 15 minutes from Show Low, this home delivers easy access to everyday essentials--shopping, dining, healthcare, and services--without living in the middle of town, so you can still relish small-town Arizona charm. Its practical location makes commuting simple and puts you in a great spot for day trips throughout the White Mountains. Competitively priced, this 4-bedroom split floor plan offers privacy and flexibility for a variety of living situations, including guests, work-from-home, or multi-generational living. The kitchen comes equipped with stainless appliances, and you'll appreciate the smart storage throughout: a coat closet, three linen closets, plus a large, secure storage area under the deck for tools, seasonal items, & outdoor gear Pinedale is a county-governed community just west of Show Low at roughly 6, 500' elevation, offering cooler temperatures and a true four-season, high-country mountain vibe. Nearby recreation includes Fool Hollow Lake and the Apache-Sitgreaves National Forests, with year-round opportunities and plentiful trails for hiking, biking, horseback riding, and OHV routes. Enjoy quick access to lakes, fishing, camping, wildlife viewing, and more.
